snippet.textDisplay: I don't know how and why I love GUJARATI language and it's art so much.... there's something that has always attracted me towards it, whether I would say Gujarati movies, or it's food, it's drama, it's colourful culture, or its music or anything, everything is just awesome.... गर्वी गुजरात छे!....but I must say, this one is a masterpiece....it is engaging and fresh... absolutely loved it🧿
snippet.textOriginal: I don't know how and why I love GUJARATI language and it's art so much.... there's something that has always attracted me towards it, whether I would say Gujarati movies, or it's food, it's drama, it's colourful culture, or its music or anything, everything is just awesome.... गर्वी गुजरात छे!....but I must say, this one is a masterpiece....it is engaging and fresh... absolutely loved it🧿
